A '''HoloNet transceiver''' was a device that allowed for communication over the [[HoloNet]]. [[Viper probe droid]]s used HoloNet transceivers to send data back to [[Imperial Navy]] [[Star Destroyer]]s.<ref name="HC 9">{{HelmetCollectionCite|9|Weapons & Uniforms}}</ref>

